===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|mongrel}}, equivalent to {{suffix|en|mong|t1=mixture|rel|pos2=pejorative diminutive}}; from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|ġemong|t=mingling}} (whence Modern English {{m|en|among}}), from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*mang-||mix}}.<ref>{{R:Online Etymology Dictionary}}</ref>

